<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q24_v15" title="Q24_v15" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>
      Se sabe que 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mi>a</m:mi>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mi>b</m:mi>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:msup>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          </m:msup>
          <m:mo>+</m:mo>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo>
          <m:mn>40</m:mn>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>, donde a y b son números enteros. ¿Cuál de los siguientes pares (a, b) es compatible con esta igualdad?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn>
            <m:mo>,</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>8</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <strong>a = 5</strong> y <strong>b = −8</strong>, entonces <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></math> y <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>·</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow></math>. Por lo tanto, <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow></math>, que no coincide con <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow></math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn>
            <m:mo>,</m:mo>
            <m:mn>8</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si <strong>a = −5</strong> y <strong>b = 8</strong>, entonces <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></math> y <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>·</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow></math>. Entonces, <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow></math>, que coincide exactamente con la igualdad dada.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
            <m:mo>,</m:mo>
            <m:mn>10</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <strong>a = −4</strong> y <strong>b = 10</strong>, entonces <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow></math> y <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>·</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow></math>. Por lo tanto, <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow></math>, que no coincide con <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow></math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mo>,</m:mo>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <strong>a = 1</strong> y <strong>b = 2</strong>, entonces <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></math>, pero <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>·</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></math>. Entonces, <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></math>, que no coincide con <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow></math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Expandir la expresión general</strong></p>
            <p>Se sabe que</p>
            <p>
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mrow>
                  <mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>)</mo>
                  <mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>)</mo>
                  <mo>=</mo>
                  <msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup>
                  <mo>+</mo>
                  <mo>(</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>)</mo>
                  <mi>x</mi>
                  <mo>+</mo>
                  <mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi>
                </mrow>
              </math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Comparar coeficientes con la igualdad dada</strong></p>
            <p>La igualdad del enunciado es</p>
            <p>
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mrow>
                  <msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup>
                  <mo>+</mo>
                  <mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi>
                  <mo>−</mo>
                  <mn>40</mn>
                </mrow>
              </math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces deben cumplirse simultáneamente:</p>
            <p>
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mrow>
                  <mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn>
                </mrow>
              </math>
              y
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mrow>
                  <mi>a</mi><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn>
                </mrow>
              </math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Buscar dos enteros cuyo producto sea −40 y cuya suma sea 3</strong></p>
            <p>Algunos pares de factores de −40 son:</p>
            <p>
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>·</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow>
              </math>
              , 
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>·</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow>
              </math>
              , 
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>·</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow>
              </math>
            </p>
            <p>Ahora revisamos sus sumas:</p>
            <p>
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow>
              </math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow>
              </math>
            </p>
            <p>
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow>
              </math>
            </p>
            <p>El par que cumple ambas condiciones es <strong>(−5, 8)</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar en la factorización</strong></p>
            <p>
              <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
                <mrow>
                  <mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>)</mo>
                  <mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>)</mo>
                  <mo>=</mo>
                  <msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup>
                  <mo>+</mo>
                  <mn>8</mn><mi>x</mi>
                  <mo>−</mo>
                  <mn>5</mn><mi>x</mi>
                  <mo>−</mo>
                  <mn>40</mn>
                  <mo>=</mo>
                  <msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup>
                  <mo>+</mo>
                  <mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi>
                  <mo>−</mo>
                  <mn>40</mn>
                </mrow>
              </math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El par compatible con la igualdad es <strong>alternativa B: (−5, 8)</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>